    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable choice for a daily driver. The exterior shows some signs of age, including several visible door dings and some thinning of the clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows noticeable wear on the driver's seat and some staining on the floor mats. Mechanically, it runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may soon require routine service for wear items like brake pads. It\u2019s a solid, functional car for someone looking for reliable transportation without the price tag of a newer model.",
