    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been well-loved and still runs like a total dream. It's in great shape and has been kept clean and tidy\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend road trip. I've really enjoyed driving it, and I'm sure you will too. Come take it for a spin and see how smoothly it handles!",
